  {
    content: 'I highly recommend Eugen to anyone seeking a talented and reliable developer. His expertise, commitment to quality, and collaborative approach make him an invaluable asset. I look forward to future opportunities to work together.',
    person: {
      name: 'Filip Lukić',
      position: 'Co-Founder of ahead&',
      avatarUrl: 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4E03AQHp5PmAqmgW0w/profile-displayphoto-shrink_200_200/0/1680120619447?e=1724889600&v=beta&t=GVU8IhpYxI489Yomt1kCj-aqGwvUTl7LRtuDiJuYi9w',
    }
  },
  {
    content: 'Very highly-skilled full stack developer. I\'m certainly looking forward to working with you again!',
    person: {
      name: 'Jaynesh Vekaria',
      position: 'Founder of MOONBEAR LTD',
      avatarUrl: 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C5603AQH0V1d37UySNw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_100_100/0/1564477552968?e=1724889600&v=beta&t=ceQ-ngPMBne0_t9i5bTG6VUCtAc0kt0cE3meHRG9ddI',
    }
  },
  {
    content: 'Eugen delivered exceptional results in building the core of our Wordpress Theme and developing a plugin for our WooCommerce checkout flow. His communication skills were outstanding, keeping us informed at every stage of the project. We are thoroughly satisfied and will definitely consider working with Eugen again in the future.',
    person: {
      name: 'Michael Wechsler',
      position: 'Product Manager at MEINE ERDE',
      avatarUrl: 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D5603AQEUe4QOTjoIpg/profile-displayphoto-shrink_100_100/0/1718912414079?e=1724889600&v=beta&t=WVIi5c9Ig76abDbCYwdhQqiMsx9AdHbVw_60b0vu0Ms',
    }
  },
  {
    content: 'Eugen was amazing and helped me to build a WordPress Plugin for my SaaS in almost no time and without real guidance from my side!',
    person: {
      name: 'Marc Zwiebler',
      position: 'Founder of KURABU',
      avatarUrl: 'https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4D03AQEtd8q5CvDbmg/profile-displayphoto-shrink_100_100/0/1642691242252?e=1724889600&v=beta&t=65hMwL59CNZ0PInYP7hgy98BYTR5T3aIIMklXFFzims',
    }
  },
]
---
<div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5">
  <div class="mt-24">
    <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight text-center">
      <span class="text-indigo-600">Client</span> reviews
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 text-center">
      Your satisfaction is the purpose of my work.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-screen-xl overflow-x-hidden mx-auto mt-10 relative">
  <div
    class="absolute w-96 h-96 blur-2xl -z-10 bg-gradient-radial from-purple-100 right-1/3 translate-x-2/3 top-10">
  </div>
    <div
      class="md:motion-safe:animate-marquee w-auto py-5 overflow-x-auto flex flex-wrap justify-center min-w-full shrink-0 items-stretch gap-10 snap-x snap-mandatory px-5">
    { reviews.map( (review, i) => <div
      class="rounded-2xl relative p-8 bg-gray-50/60 backdrop-blur-md transition-all ring-1 ring-gray-200/50 shadow hover:shadow-lg w-[calc(100vw-5.75rem)] max-w-md flex flex-col justify-between snap-start snap-always shrink-0 first-of-type:scroll-m-10 scroll-m-5">
      <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl [text-wrap:balance]">
        {review.content}
      </blockquote>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-10">
        <div class="shrink-0">
          <picture>
            <img
              src={review.person.avatarUrl}
              class="rounded-full w-12 h-12 object-cover bg-slate-100"
              alt={review.person.name}
              loading="lazy"
              width="48"
              height="48"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </picture>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-medium text-slate-800">{review.person.name}</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">{review.person.position}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> ) }
